                  "revisionId": 2721498,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Transient Fortitude 's negative Ability Duration of 27.5% will be rounded up to 28%. Therefore, Continuity will give a +2% in Ability Duration , Constitution will simply negate its effects, and Primed Continuity will give a +27% Ability Duration at max rank."
                }
              },
