                  "pageId": 571679,
                  "revisionId": 2721498,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Can be stacked with Blind Rage , Intensify , Augur Secrets and Power Drift to provide a total of +223% Ability Strength , and 259% with all three Umbral mods ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
